pub trait Summary {
    fn summarize(&self) -> String;
}

slides.content:
Once the Trait exists, you can explicitly implement it for a specific Struct using `impl Trait for Type`.

```rust
pub struct Article { pub text: String }

impl Summary for Article {
    fn summarize(&self) -> String {
        format!("Read: {}", self.text)
    }
}
```
